          <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
          <h2 class="section-heading">A filmmaker with a passion for visual storytelling</h2>
          <p>With years of experience behind the lens, I specialize in creating cinematic experiences that resonate with audiences. From concept to final cut, I bring a meticulous eye for detail and an unwavering commitment to the craft.</p>
          <p>Whether it's a narrative short, a brand campaign, or a documentary, I believe every project deserves a unique visual voice. I work closely with clients and collaborators to ensure that each frame serves the story.</p>
